profile:
Moving is a big hassle as it is and when that move is a long-distance one, such as cross-country, then it can be an even more daunting challenge. Luckily, Bob’s Your Mover is here to help! With over 42 years of experience in the moving industry, Bob takes pride in his customer service. He is based in Chilliwack and long-distance moving is his specialty. Never worry again about the stress of moving your life across the country.

****
 
Bob takes the time to answer any questions you have and make sure you know everything is being handled well. If you want to go to the scale with him to check your quote is for the correct amount, you are more than welcome to do so. He is there with you every step of the way so you don’t have to worry about a thing. Bob will be the only person you deal with, so you can get to know him very well.

****
 
Bob’s main goal and value is to provide a service that ensures you can be stress-free without any worries, including packing services, which are available upon request. Bob’s Your Mover and he is with you for the long haul. Don’t hire the shady moving companies who can change their prices on you without warning. You don’t know what you’re getting. Instead, hire Bob and he’ll treat you right. Contact him today and book your move today. Bob recommends setting up well in advance so you are ensured of getting the time you want.
specialities: We specialize on long distance moves
payment_method: Visa, MC, E-Transfer, Cash, Certified Cheques
